data.description: Assumable 3.375% mortgage on this gorgeous home.  This heart of Fishers professionally designed pristine townhome, boasts 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, & 2 half baths. Family room features a gas fireplace & new built-ins while the updated kitchen will delight any chef. Large Den/Library/Office on first level with adjacent bathroom.  Can be converted to a bedroom for minimal cost.  Updated laundry room w/ granite & new lighting throughout the house. On the lower level, an added powder bath w/ a plumbed drain for a shower offers ensuite for a third bedroom or office. Upstairs, you'll find the vaulted ceilings in the remaining two bedrooms, each w/ its ensuite & walk-in closet. Garage built-ins stay. This dog-friendly neighborhood has fantastic neighbors. The community has an entrance to Nickel Plate Trail to walk or bike to downtown Fishers!  Previous Buyer was not approved for a loan and this townhome is back on the market!
